</i></p>
<p><i>Economist</i>, 30 August 2014. 
</p>
<p> 14 See Stern and Berger, <i>ISIS: The State of Terror</i>. 
</p>
<p> 15 See &#8220;Rule of terror&#8221;, paras. 17 and 29. See also Stern and Berger, <i>ISIS: The State of Terror</i>, which 
</p>
<p>notes that in an article in <i>Dabiq</i>, the online English-language magazine of ISIL, it asked for doctors, 
</p>
<p>engineers, scholars and people with military, administrative and service expertise.  
</p>
<p> 16 See Saltman and Winter, <i>Islamic State</i>. 
</p>
