</p>
<p>&#8220;an intentional mass killing of civilians not directly participating in hostilities, or hors de combat 
</p>
<p>fighters, by organized armed forces or groups in a single incident, in violation of international human 
</p>
<p>rights or humanitarian law&#8221;. See A/HRC/28/69, annex II, para. 1. 
</p>
