</p>
<p>from-tight-standards-on-civilian-deaths-183724795.html. 
</p>
<p> 103 See A/68/389, paras. 69&#8211;72. 
</p>
<p> 104 See Nils Melzer, &#8220;Interpretive guidance on the notion of direct participation in hostilities under 
</p>
